<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Travel Stories | Dark Destinations</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.5/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gloock&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans&family=Exile&family=Tagesschrift&family=EB+Garamond&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Akaya+Kanadaka&family=Averia+Libre:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,700&family=Creepster&family=Diplomata&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400..800;1,400..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body {
      /* background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1b1b1b 20%, #0a0a0a); */
      color: #f5f5f5;
      /* font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; */
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    header {
      padding: 4rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #111;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Gloock', serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: #fa334a;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #bbb;
    }

    .story-section {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .story-card {
      background-color: #1f1f1f;
      border-left: 5px solid #fc475c;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      /* box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 76, 96, 0.1); */
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .story-card:hover {
      background-color: #222222;
    }

    .story-title {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ff3c53;
    }

    .story-meta {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #999;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .story-content {
      color: #ddd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../includes/navbar.ejs") %>

  <header>
    <h1>Traveler Tales</h1>
    <p>Real experiences from brave souls who've walked the haunted paths.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-card">
      <h2 class="story-title">Whispers from the Chillingham Castle</h2>
      <div class="story-meta">By Amanda Grey | Jan 2025</div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <p>One cold December evening, I spent the night in the infamous Chillingham Castle in England. I heard whispers in my room, despite being alone. The air turned icy, and I saw a shadowy figure glide past the window... despite the fact it was the second floor. My recording captured faint murmurs in old English dialect...</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-card">
      <h2 class="story-title">The Screams of Bhangarh</h2>
      <div class="story-meta">By Rajiv Mehta | Oct 2024</div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <p>My friends and I dared to enter Bhangarh Fort after sunset. We never expected to hear blood-curdling screams echoing through the ruins. One of us fainted. Locals warned us before, but we thought they exaggerated. They didn’t. Never again.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-card">
      <h2 class="story-title">An Encounter in the Stanley Hotel</h2>
      <div class="story-meta">By Emily Dawson | Jul 2024</div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <p>As a horror writer, I always wanted to visit the Stanley Hotel in Colorado. I didn’t expect to hear piano notes at 3 AM when no one was in the lobby. My door kept unlocking by itself. The ghost tour guide later told me that room 217 has a history of... "playful residents." I’m a believer now.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include("../includes/footer.ejs") %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.5/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
